{"prompt": "Generate a website for a online magazine. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Corporate Online Magazine</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Dark blue */\n            --secondary-color: #E0E0E0; /* Light grey */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --header-footer-bg: #F8F8F8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-align: center;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #0056b3; /* Lighter shade of primary */\n        }\n\n        main {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        .featured-article {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .featured-article h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .featured-article p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .article-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .article-item {\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .article-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .article-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .article-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        .read-more {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .read-more:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Corporate Insight</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#featured\">Featured</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#business\">Business</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#technology\">Technology</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#finance\">Finance</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#opinion\">Opinion</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"featured\" class=\"featured-article\">\n            <h2>The Future of Remote Work: Navigating the Hybrid Landscape</h2>\n            <p>Explore the evolving dynamics of the modern workplace, where flexibility and productivity intertwine. Our latest analysis delves into strategies for successful hybrid models.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"articles\">\n            <h2>Latest Articles</h2>\n            <div class=\"article-list\">\n                <article class=\"article-item\">\n                    <h3>AI's Impact on Market Trends</h3>\n                    <p>An in-depth look at how artificial intelligence is reshaping market analysis and forecasting, providing unprecedented insights for businesses.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </article>\n\n                <article class=\"article-item\">\n                    <h3>Sustainable Business Practices</h3>\n                    <p>Discover innovative approaches to corporate social responsibility and how sustainability is becoming a key driver of business value and consumer trust.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </article>\n\n                <article class=\"article-item\">\n                    <h3>Global Economic Outlook for 2024</h3>\n                    <p>Expert analysis on the key factors influencing the global economy, from geopolitical shifts to technological advancements and their impact on various sectors.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </article>\n\n                <article class=\"article-item\">\n                    <h3>The Rise of the Gig Economy</h3>\n                    <p>Examining the growing trend of freelance and contract work, its implications for traditional employment, and how companies are adapting.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                </article>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Corporate Insight. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}